title: SVENGOOLIE - Tarantulas:The Deadly Cargo-1977 aired 2-17-18
description:
SVENGOOLIE : If you're here, then you know who he is. https://svengoolie.com/

PLOT : Townsfolk unite against deadly spiders freed from a crashed plane's coffee-bean cargo.

Cast:
Claude Akins(ouch!-you'll get it later) 
Tom Atkins (The Fog, Creepshow, Night of the Creeps)
Pat Hingle (Tim Burton's Batman- Quick and The Dead, etc. countless roles)
Howard Hesseman ( WKRP In Cincinnati, Head of the Class)
Charles Siebert (Trapper John MD)


If you should read this: I used a dvd print of the movie and adhered closely as possible to the Sven broadcast, while keeping all that was edited out for time purposes, Intact.

As an " Extra" , I included the Ridiculous End Credits / Epilogue / Unused Footage containing Incredibleably Awful music. Think Barney Miller gone bad.....
And as this was originally done for a bud of mine, I added some Text overlays...
Purists, the dvd of what I used is out there--(sorry for not having the uploaders name for credit).

Special Guest Interview : Dana Gould

I hope you enjoy. Life's busy and I'm not here as often as I'd Like. 
I'll share more asap.
